OL,3,CJersey's government reveals 2023
OL,4,Ctravel expenses
OL,6,FThe Government of Jersey has finally
OL,7,Fpublished its long-awaited travel
OL,8,Fexpenses for 2023 - which reportedly
OL,9,Fincluded flying an invasive species
OL,10,Fexpert over from Honolulu in Hawaii.
OL,12,FThe costs for 2023 totalled more than
OL,13,F#350,000, with trips including:
OL,15,FThe details, which have only just been
OL,16,Fpublished, cover the period when
OL,17,FDeputy Kristina Moore was still Chief
OL,18,FMinister.
