OL,6,FHowever, critics question the value of
OL,7,Fsuch trips, especially during concerns
OL,8,Fover the climate and the cost of
OL,9,Fliving crisis.
OL,11,FDeputy Max Andrews, of St Helier
OL,12,FNorth, tells ITV News: "In the world
OL,13,Fof remote working, you'd expect there
OL,14,Fwould be more online meetings.
OL,16,F"We can talk to people without the
OL,17,Fneed for travel. We're just incurring
OL,18,Fcosts that we can't afford to."
