OL,6,FHowever, Deputy Andrews understands
OL,7,Fwhy training for frontline workers may
OL,8,Fneed to be delivered in person and
OL,9,Fbelieves such expenditure is
OL,10,Fjustified, depending on the
OL,11,Fcircumstances.
OL,13,FFormer Senator Ted Vibert is most
OL,14,Fconcerned by reports of politicians,
OL,15,Fother than the External Relations
OL,16,FMinister, representing Jersey on
OL,17,Fforeign trips.
