OL,6,FHe expalins: "What they say about
OL,7,Fthese meetings is that it enables them
OL,8,Fto get a global view of everything,
OL,9,Fbut you can do that watching
OL,10,Ftelevision.
OL,12,F"You really don't need to go anywhere
OL,13,Fto do that - it's ridiculous."
OL,15,FThe newly published costs are separate
OL,16,Ffrom more than #35,000 of taxpayers'
OL,17,Fmoney spent in 2023 on off-island
OL,18,Fevents organised by the Commonwealth
OL,19,FParliamentary Association.
